title: Anne of Green Gables
creator: Lucy Maud Montgomery
description: LibriVox recording of Anne of Green Gables by Lucy Maud Montgomery. Read by Karen Savage. The timeless story of the young orphan girl sent by accident to a brother and sister who had wanted a boy, Anne, with her vivid imagination and sensitive spirit, has enchanted readers for generations. (Summary by Karen Savage) M4B audiobook of complete book
subject: librivox; audiobook; anne; green gables; fiction
source: Librivox recording of a public-domain text

reviews.reviewbody: I'm extremely obliged to you for reading this wonderful book. You have such a sweet voice, it was so pleasant to listen. I hope that you'll record more.
